netInt.containers

Class SubContainer

  • java.lang.Object
    • netInt.containers.Container
      • netInt.containers.SubContainer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class SubContainer
extends Container
implements java.io.Serializable
    Instances of SubContainer are Containers of references to Nodes and Edges and their visual representations, i.e. the corresponding VNodes and VEdges. Thus all visual elements included in instances of SubContainer are the visual representations of Nodes and Edges instantiated in the root graph.
    Author:
    juan salamanca
